examples.en: The local currency is the Swiss franc.

examples.en: The Swiss dealer offered $2 million for the painting.

examples.en: Nearly 80% of Swiss citizens on average turn out to vote.

examples.en: The Swiss entrepreneur has pulled the plug on any further investment in the firm.

examples.en: The money was lodged in a Swiss bank account.
examples.ru: Деньги были размещены в швейцарском банке.
